{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextareacomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent08TextAreaB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of text area","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTextArea"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"TextAreaComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"text area"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text area","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for text area component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text area component tokens you want.","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingBlockXl }","        override var sizeMinHeightInput: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._1000 }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider: TextAreaComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(textArea: CustomTextAreaComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own space and size semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let textAreaComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider(","                                            sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                            spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B36ThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","title":"OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider"},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextAreaComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:spac